---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 112
By: Marsilio Ficino
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Consummation of Desire
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Uncreate Source of Beauty
---
For all things the primal good is the cause of their being good. Therefore it
is the cause of their being desired. But if for its sake all things are to be
desired, consequently itself is to be desired more than all things and by all
things.
